{"about_the_game":"Tinker Pilot is a VR space sim built from the ground up for <strong>maximum immersion</strong>. Use your motion controllers, HOTAS or your own custom cockpit and take full control of your ship.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Engaging Gameplay</h2>The gameplay in Tinker Pilot is meant to be diverse and challenging, but above all is <strong>meant to be fun</strong>. Complete different missions and challenges in a <strong>realistic physics</strong> environment where the proximity to terrain, stations, ships, and other objects gives a <strong>greater sense of movement and speed</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/gameplay_wide_median.gif?t=1690653658\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Exhaustive Ship Systems</h2>Every ship system is designed as an <strong>interface</strong> with a series of actions and data that can be accessed from your cockpit. Take full control over every thruster, sensor, stabilizer or any ship component and <strong>make your piloting as complex as you like</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/slowdown_wide_median.gif?t=1690653658\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">1:1 Philosophy</h2>Tinker Pilot has been designed with 1:1 immersion at its core to achieve the <strong>maximum sense of presence</strong> you can get. <strong>Use any combination of input methods</strong> (HOTAS, VR motion controllers, hand tracking, etc.) and your spaceship cockpit will be adapted to to ensure there's no mismatch between what you <i>see</i> and what you <i>feel</i>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/interaction_wide_median.gif?t=1690653658\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cockpit customization</h2>Whether you want a layout that adapts to your piloting style, a virtual representation of your real devices or just some decoration, th